t: Fatawi al-shaykh bakhit al-muti'i : mufti al-diyar al-misriyah sabiqan.al-juzu al-awwal
Qanun daman haqq al-husul 'ala al-ma'lumat fi al-urdun : dirasah muqaranah ma' al-ma'ayir al-dawliyah
Al-irhab bayna al-fiqh al-islami wa-al-qanun al-dawli
Al-jarauim al-iliktruniyah al-waqi'ah 'ala al-'ird bayna al-shari'ah wa-al-qanun al-muqaran
Al-himayah al-jinauiyah li-naql wa-zira'at al-a'dau al-bashariyah bayna al-shari'ah wa-al-qanun al-muqaran
Al-tazwir : al-usus al-'ilmiyah li-muqaranah al-khutut al-yadawiyah
Huquq al-insan bayna al-tashri' al-islami wa-al-qawanin al-wad'iyah : dirasah fiqhiyah muqaranah
